          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 mb-6 leading-tight tracking-tight font-serif">
            Peak Performance <br class="hidden sm:block" />
            <span class="text-gradient from-amber-600 via-orange-500 to-red-600">for Founders</span>
          </h1>

